						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1493 (1571 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Seems to record a grant of some land as <hi rend="italic">tiruviḷaiyāṭṭam for</hi> offerings to the god. Mentions Vīravalli Aṇṇaṅgār. The record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1493, Prajōtpatti, Vṛiśchika, śū. 12 which may be equated with 1571 A.D., November 28.</hi></p>						

